LLVM standard C++ library
  svn co http://llvm.org/svn/llvm-project/libcxx/trunk

LLVM C++ ABI implementation library
  svn co http://llvm.org/svn/llvm-project/libcxxabi/trunk

PathScale C++ ABI implementation library
  git clone https://github.com/pathscale/libcxxrt.git

C++ exceptions and stack unwinding library
  git clone git://git.sv.gnu.org/libunwind.git
